### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### List semua item AHSP
GET http://localhost:8081/ahsp
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Detail satu item AHSP
GET http://localhost:8081/ahsp/AHSP.CK.001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### List wilayah tersedia
GET http://localhost:8081/regions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Hitung HSP satu item — dinding bata (AHSP.CK.001) wilayah Jawa Tengah
POST http://localhost:8081/rab/hsp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.001",
  "region_code": "jateng"
}

###

### Hitung HSP — plesteran (AHSP.CK.002)
POST http://localhost:8081/rab/hsp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.002",
  "region_code": "jateng"
}

###

### Hitung RAB — 2 item (nilai acuan: subtotal = 11.411.620)
POST http://localhost:8081/rab/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region_code": "jateng",
  "ppn_rate": 0.11,
  "lines": [
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.001", "volume": 50},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.002", "volume": 50}
  ]
}

###

### Hitung RAB — 4 item lengkap dengan durasi (nilai acuan: subtotal = 77.606.320)
POST http://localhost:8081/rab/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region_code": "jateng",
  "ppn_rate": 0.11,
  "lines": [
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.001", "volume": 120, "duration_days": 6},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.002", "volume": 240, "duration_days": 8},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.003", "volume": 18,  "duration_days": 5},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.004", "volume": 85,  "duration_days": 7}
  ]
}

###

### Kurva S — sequential, mingguan (total 26 hari, 4 periode)
POST http://localhost:8081/schedule/s-curve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region_code": "jateng",
  "ppn_rate": 0.11,
  "period_days": 7,
  "mode": "sequential",
  "lines": [
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.001", "volume": 120, "duration_days": 6},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.002", "volume": 240, "duration_days": 8},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.003", "volume": 18,  "duration_days": 5},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.004", "volume": 85,  "duration_days": 7}
  ]
}

###

### Kurva S — parallel
POST http://localhost:8081/schedule/s-curve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region_code": "jateng",
  "ppn_rate": 0.11,
  "period_days": 7,
  "mode": "parallel",
  "lines": [
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.001", "volume": 120, "duration_days": 6},
    {"ahsp_code": "AHSP.CK.002", "volume": 240, "duration_days": 8}
  ]
}

###

### ERROR TEST: AHSP code tidak ada → harus 400
POST http://localhost:8081/rab/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region_code": "jateng",
  "lines": [{"ahsp_code": "TIDAK_ADA", "volume": 10}]
}

###

### ERROR TEST: item AHSP tidak ditemukan → harus 404
GET http://localhost:8081/ahsp/TIDAK_ADA
Content-Type: application/json
